items.description:

There have been many controversies about the training and use of art style models, but they are also a difficult part to avoid in the process of AI painting progress.

Therefore, it is recommended to use such art style models as a kind of existence similar to potions, by matching Loras of different art styles with different weights to form images with different styles (although this may lead to bad results, it is worth trying).Alternatively, it can be used to match your favorite character models. Anyway, I hope not to compare it with the artist's own work and make rude remarks, which will harm the community's environment.

At the same time, there are still many problems to be discovered in this model. In short, hope you have a good time.

items.name: Banksy Style
items.description:
Banksy is a pseudonymous British street artist and political activist known for his distinctive stencil-based artwork and provocative social commentary.

Banksy's style is characterized by its satirical and subversive nature. His artwork often combines dark humor, powerful imagery, and thought-provoking messages. Banksy uses stencils to create his artworks quickly and anonymously on various surfaces, such as walls, buildings, and public spaces.

His subject matter often includes political and social issues, such as war, poverty, consumerism, and government surveillance. Banksy's artwork challenges the status quo and questions authority, aiming to stimulate conversation and raise awareness about societal injustices.

Banksy's identity remains a mystery, and he maintains a high level of anonymity, rarely appearing in public or revealing his face. His art has gained international acclaim and has become highly sought after by collectors.

In addition to his street art, Banksy has also created installations, sculptures, and other forms of artwork. He has staged several high-profile art interventions, including the shredding of his own artwork at an auction, which further emphasizes his subversive approach to art and the art market.

Banksy's work has had a significant impact on contemporary art and has inspired a new generation of street artists and activists. His ability to use art as a tool for social and political commentary has sparked conversations and challenged traditional notions of art and its role in society.

Despite the elusive nature of his identity, Banksy's influence and relevance continue to grow. His artworks carry a powerful message and serve as a reminder of the power of art to ignite change and provoke critical thinking.

items.name: 王冰冰Lora 高质量精炼
items.description:
推荐权重：

0.8~1.2(通用模型)

0.3~0.7(面部特写模型)

1.0~1.8(融合模型)

【通用模型】

百搭模型，泛化性强，tag识别度很高

【面部特写模型】

从通用模型生成的图片中筛选高质量脸部，再次训练，如此往复，达到高质量面部特写的效果。但tag识别度较低，由于训练素材中去除了背景和杂色，如需添加背景或让图像颜色更丰富，可能需要提高相关提示词的权重。此类模型专注面部特写，可能会有美颜过重的感觉，并且不擅长处理脸部面积过小的图片，写tag时尽量使脸部长宽达到图片宽度的1/3以上（谨慎使用诸如full body等减少面部权重的tag）

【融合模型】

就是前两个模型按1:1的比例Merge的版本，集合了两者各自的优点，强推！！

items.name: Ines Fujin (umamusume)
items.description:
LoHa of Ines Fujin (umamusume). Please install extension on WebUI.

After installing extension, put LoHa file in your sd/models/lora folder and write LoRA notation in prompt to applying LoHa. <lora:your_loha_name:weight>

All of my works is free. If you'd like to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. 👍

NOTICE

  • After careful consideration, I decided not to produce LoRA of the characters below.

    • Otonashi Etsuko

    • Akasaka Misato

    • Hosoe Junko

  • If anyone wants the characters above, I will consider making them.

  • Except for the above, I will make the rest of the characters in umamusume unless there is a special notice.

Recommended options

  • LoRA weight around 0.7

  • Trigger words

    • Base

      • ines fujin \(umamusume\)

    • Original Art :

      • single ear cover, visor cap, freckles, track jacket, cleavage, pleated skirt, bike shorts, shorts under skirt, black socks, sneakers

    • Racing competition costume :

      • single ear cover, visor cap, freckles, choker, collarbone, pink jacket, crop top, cropped jacket, short sleeves, wristband, midriff, navel, white belt, pink skirt, miniskirt, bike shorts, shorts under skirt, black shorts, black socks, shoes, pink footwear

    • Casual :

      • casual, single ear cover, brown headwear, baseball cap, freckles, hair through headwear, ears through headwear, hood down, orange hoodie, drawstring, cropped hoodie, crop top overhang, bodystocking, long sleeves, wirstwatch, black pants, track pants, brown footwear

    • Valentine :

      • official alternate costume, maid headdress, hair ornament, necklace, jewelry, white shirt, clothing cutout, shoulder cutout, short sleeves, heart, wrist cuffs, red apron, plaid skirt, white socks, red footwear, mary janes

    • Tracen summer uniform :

      • tracen school uniform, summer uniform, serafuku, puffy short sleeves, purple bowtie, horseshoe ornament, sailor collar, sailor shirt, purple shirt, white skirt, pleated skirt, frilled skirt, miniskirt, zettai ryouiki, white thighhighs, brown footwear, loafers

    • Tracen winter uniform :

      • tracen school uniform, winter uniform, puffy long sleeves, sailor collar, sailor shirt, purple shirt, white bowtie, horseshoe ornament, purple skirt, frills, brown footwear, loafers

Use a model derived from or mixed with animefull model.

  • Settings

    • Stable Diffusion WebUI by Automatic1111

    • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

    • about 20 steps, CFG scale 3.5~6.5

    • I recommend kl-f8-anime2.vae

    • CLIP skip = 1

    • Use Hires.fix to get higher quality image

      • Upscaler

        • Latent, Latent (nearest-exact), Latent (bicubic antialiased) or other Latent series.

      • Denoising strength 0.50~0.65

LoRA training info

  • trained on sd-scripts by kohya_ss.

    • LyCORIS by KohakuBlueleaf

    • Thank you all a lot!

  • based on Animefull-pruned model

  • 202 images consist of

    • 4x low quality 78 images

    • 8x medium quality 74 images

    • 16x high quality 50 images

    • => 1 epoch = 1704 images

  • replaced character feature tags with ines fujin \(umamusume\)

    • 1girl, blunt bangs, medium hair, horse tail, bangs, horse girl, simple background, animal ears, long hair, brown hair, diagonal bangs, official alternate costume, solo, black hair, horse ears, short hair, side ponytail, green eyes, sidelocks, yellow eyes, one side up, alternate costume, parted bangs

    • I think these tags are the essentials of Ines Fujin or

    • unnecessary for training because of duplication.

  • resolution : 768x768 with aspect ratio bucketing.

  • other training settings is included in training data or metadata of LoRA file.

All uploaded images are generated by AOM3A1

And, special thanks to my best friend. DH.

items.name: Beeple (Mike Winkelmann) Style
items.description:
Beeple, whose real name is Mike Winkelmann, is an American digital artist known for his groundbreaking work in the field of digital art and his influential contributions to the NFT (non-fungible token) art movement.

Beeple's style can be described as futuristic, surreal, and often politically charged. He creates highly detailed and visually stunning digital artworks, often combining elements of science fiction, pop culture, and social commentary. His pieces often explore themes such as technology, consumerism, and the human condition.

One of Beeple's notable projects is "Everydays: The First 5000 Days," in which he created and shared a new artwork every day for 5,000 consecutive days. This ambitious endeavor showcases his dedication to his craft and his ability to consistently produce thought-provoking and visually striking works.

Beeple gained significant attention in 2021 when he sold a digital artwork titled "Everydays: The First 5000 Days" as an NFT for a record-breaking price at auction. This sale brought widespread recognition to the world of digital art and catapulted Beeple into the mainstream art scene.

His use of digital tools and software to create his artwork has pushed the boundaries of what is possible in the realm of digital art. His skillful blending of digital techniques, intricate details, and bold concepts has inspired countless artists and has solidified his position as one of the most influential digital artists of our time.

Beeple's art has become synonymous with the NFT art movement, which has revolutionized the art world by utilizing blockchain technology to establish unique ownership and provenance for digital artworks. His success has paved the way for other digital artists to explore new possibilities in the realm of art and technology.

Mike Winkelmann, aka Beeple, has left an indelible mark on the digital art landscape, demonstrating the power of digital creativity and challenging traditional notions of art ownership and distribution. His innovative work continues to inspire and shape the future of digital art.

items.name: Durandal-Palatinus Equinox-Honkai 3rd
items.description:
v3

中文

全新的训练数据，第一次尝试把两个服装融进一个lora里。训练时保留了一部分服装tag以获得更稳定的输出和更容易地换装，结果确实令人惊喜。推荐权重0.8，想要改变外观只需要保留daie white/daie black及头发相关提示词，并且降低权重到0.6左右即可。如果换装时发色也变了的话添加"blonde hair"即可。对于黑色外观，添加armored boots有很大概率是全身图，即使添加cowboy shot也不能获得相应的图像，需要去除armored boots。同时，有概率出现其他穿着铠甲的人，对于这个问题，解决办法是不要让她干巴巴的站着(standing)，添加一些其他的描述，比如背景，姿势，动作等。训练素材为纯黑背景，一般需要添加背景描述词。在真实模型上也能有一定程度的表现，如果你会分层使用lora，则可获得更好的图像。

English

Brand new training data, the first attempt to integrate two clothing into one lora. A part of the clothing tag was kept during training to obtain a more stable output and make it easier to change clothes. The result is indeed surprising. The recommended weight is 0.8. If you want to change the appearance, you only need to keep daie white/daie black and hair-related prompts, and reduce the weight to about 0.6. If the hair color also changes when changing clothes, just add "blonde hair".For the black appearance, adding armored boots has a high probability of being a full-body image, even if adding cowboy shot, the corresponding image cannot be obtained, so you need to remove armored boots. At the same time, there is a probability that other people wearing armor will appear. For this problem, the solution is not to let her stand lonely, but to add some other descriptions, such as background, posture, action, etc.The training material is a pure black background, and background descriptors generally need to be added.It can also have a certain degree of performance on the real model. If you can use lora layered, you can get a better image.

items.name: chillySauceMix
items.description:
This is an attempt to make a free/open available model.

If you like my work, feel free to buy me a coffee at ko-fi. https://ko-fi.com/mixboy

The following models are used by PoV Skin Texture - r34 Lucid Black (this model is used by the ChilloutMix as described)

All models have merged with the SuperMerger extension

  • pyro's_pov models - (pyro_pov_a + pyro_pov_b)

  • analogDiffusion_10 (Fp16)

  • F222 (Fp32) see also F222 at https://rentry.co/sdmodels

  • r34_e4 (Fp16) - from https://rentry.co/sdmodels

  • neverendingDreamNED_noVae (Fp32) by @Lykon

Merge Recipe

Merging steps: (please see also https://rentry.org/hdgrecipes recipes.)

Merging Steps are modified recipe of https://rentry.org/hdgrecipes#instructions_4

  • pyro_pov_a + pyro_pov_b = pyAB

  • analogDiffusion_10 x 0.85 + pyAB x 0.15 = MERGE1

  • MERGE1 x 0.95 + v1-5-pruned-emaonly x 0.05 = MERGE1Fix

  • MERGE1Fix+ (F222_v1 - v1-5-pruned-emaonly) x 1 = MERGE2

  • MERGE2 x 0.75 + r34_e4 x 0.25 = MERGE_BASE

Now we can get MERGE_BASE named ChillyMixBaseV0.

but, the ChillyMixBaseV0 model alone is not good enough to use. It produces overfitted results sometimes. To remedy this issue, simply merge a good model like the NED(NeverEndingDream - NO VAE version).

  • ChillyMixBaseV0 x (1 - alpha) + neverendingDreamNED_noVae x alpha

the alpha could be 0.4 ~ 0.6 value.

alpha = 0.6 is chosen and named ChillySauceMix.

What's the difference

What are the advantages of this unlike anything other models?

  • first, its recipe is open, anyone who wants to change the results a bit can change their recipe based on it.

  • more realistic body/skin

  • less realistic face : r32_e4 + NED contribute to it.

  • less Asian style - you can use the PureErosFace(v1) embedding for Asian women.

Useful AUTOMATIC1111's webui extensions

  • SuperMerger extension

  • Lora Block Weight extension

  • webui model toolkit to examine Loras and models.

  • civitai extension to add several useful features for civitai.

License

Like as ChillyMix, its license has no commercial restriction. it is open and free:

CreativeML-Open Rail-M

This model permits users to:

✔Use the model without crediting the creator

✔Sell images they generate

✔Run on services that generate images for money

✔Share merges using this model

✔Sell this model or merges using this model

✔Have different permissions when sharing merges

Support me

If you like my work, feel free to buy me a coffee at ko-fi. https://ko-fi.com/mixboy
